name: 2. Information
3. The same period
query:
MATCH (where)<-[:LIVED_IN]-(trex:Dinosaur {name: "Tyrannosaurus"})-[:LIVED_DURING]->(when:Period)

MATCH (where)<-[li:LIVED_IN]-(dinos:Dinosaur)-[ld:LIVED_DURING]->(when)

RETURN dinos, li, where, ld, when

name: 4. The same time
query:
MATCH (where)<-[:LIVED_IN]-(trex:Dinosaur {name: "Tyrannosaurus"})-[trex_ld:LIVED_DURING]->(when:Period)

MATCH (where)<-[li:LIVED_IN]-(dinos:Dinosaur)-[ld:LIVED_DURING]->(when)
WHERE 
  trex_ld.from < ld.from and
  trex_ld.to > ld.to

RETURN trex, dinos, li, where, ld, when

name: 5. Years to Stegasaurus
query:
MATCH (steg:Dinosaur {name: "Stegosaurus"})-[steg_ld:LIVED_DURING]-()
MATCH (dino:Dinosaur)-[ld:LIVED_DURING]-()
RETURN dino.name, ld.from, ld.to, ld.to - steg_ld.from AS millionsYearsTillSteg, dino.link
ORDER by millionsYearsTillSteg
